{{flavour|Summon a hell sentinel, a nightmarish edifice of animated hate.}}
'''Summon Hell Sentinel''' is a monster-only spell that summons a single [[hell sentinel]].

{{monsters with spell}}

Dispater can sustain up to 3 monsters with this spell.

==History==
*Summon Hell Sentinel spell was added in [[0.27]].

